{"tid":1299340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請幫手推] 5年前，5個學生代表坐係林鄭對面理性對話，最後4個判囚","createTime":"2019-07-09T04:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T05:39:31.000Z","uid":54373,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"58e81182c124a05bde140bbdeab98b81e3a41066","tid":1299340,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"談判？<br />\n<br />\n5年前，5個學生代表坐係林鄭對面，最後4個判囚。而林鄭月娥左一句Nathan，右一句Eason，最後步步高昇，做埋特首。5年後，同一個人再玩多次？談你老母。<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰：判監8個月；後終院上訴得直，重判上訴120小時社會服務令（926衝擊公民廣場案）<br />\n<br />\n周永康：判監7個月；後終院上訴得直，判3星期監禁，緩刑1年（926衝擊公民廣場案）<br />\n<br />\n岑敖暉：判監1個月、緩刑1年，罰款1萬元（雨傘旺角清場刑事藐視法庭案）<br />\n<br />\n鍾耀華：判監8個月、緩刑2年（佔中九子案）<br />\n<br />\n註：開會中的計時員，獲賞連任嶺南大學「校長」。"},{"pid":"978a9990a22fa7543b13974d0ea10b73a70a31b2","tid":1299340,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d2e772925b8662f13cb793c27b76fbbeab5d87","tid":1299340,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6257312986708a812209fbe6e314902fdd86da1b","tid":1299340,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed40c7dfff6d50e817094b9b3d4aa6a87966ef5b","tid":1299340,"uid":181727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e87d36db03e1af18a387f12f501f7a454b2dcd","tid":1299340,"uid":32151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"表面同你傾 實質背後陰你"},{"pid":"13794292644cf541c5ca23780d9ed3472389750a","tid":1299340,"uid":265959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:20:48.000Z","msg"